    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r] ON [u].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
    WHERE [u].[Username] = @__decodedJWTModel_Username_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w] ON [t].[Id] = [w].[UploaderId]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w0] ON [t].[Id] = [w0].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [t].[Id] = [l].[LikerId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [w].[Id], [w0].[Id]

SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[ActiveToken], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[HashedPassword], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[ProfileImage], [u].[RegisterDate], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Username], [r].[Id], [r].[Title]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[ActiveToken], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[HashedPassword], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[ProfileImage], [u].[RegisterDate], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Username], [r].[Id] AS [Id0], [r].[Title]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r] ON [u].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
    WHERE [u].[Username] = @__decodedJWTModel_Username_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w] ON [t].[Id] = [w].[UploaderId]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w0] ON [t].[Id] = [w0].[UserId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[ActiveToken], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[HashedPassword], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[ProfileImage], [u].[RegisterDate], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Username], [r].[Id] AS [Id0], [r].[Title]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r] ON [u].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
    WHERE [u].[Username] = @__decodedJWTModel_Username_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w] ON [t].[Id] = [w].[UploaderId]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w0] ON [t].[Id] = [w0].[UserId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveToken], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HashedPassword], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastName], [t].[ProfileImage], [t].[RegisterDate], [t].[RoleId], [t].[Username], [t].[Id0], [t].[Title], [w].[Id], [w].[Description], [w].[DownloadsCount], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[Source], [w].[Title], [w].[UploaderId], [w].[UserId], [w].[ViewsCount], [w].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [w0].[Id], [w0].[Description], [w0].[DownloadsCount], [w0].[PublishDate], [w0].[Source], [w0].[Title], [w0].[UploaderId], [w0].[UserId], [w0].[ViewsCount], [w0].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [l].[Id], [l].[LikerId], [l].[WallpaperId]

) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [w].[Id], [w].[Description], [w].[DownloadsCount], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[Source], [w].[Title], [w].[UploaderId], [w].[UserId], [w].[ViewsCount], [w].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[ActiveToken], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[HashedPassword], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[ProfileImage], [u].[RegisterDate], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Username], [w0].[Id] AS [Id1], [w0].[Title] AS [Title0]
    FROM [Wallpapers] AS [w]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [w].[UploaderId] = [u].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [WallpaperGenreCategories] AS [w0] ON [w].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId] = [w0].[Id]
    WHERE [w].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [t].[Id] = [l].[WallpaperId]
LEFT JOIN [WallpaperImages] AS [w1] ON [t].[Id] = [w1].[WallpaperId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [l].[Id]

FROM [Wallpapers] AS [w]
INNER JOIN [WallpaperGenreCategories] AS [w0] ON [w].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId] = [w0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [w].[UploaderId] = [u].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [WallpaperImages] AS [w1] ON [w].[Id] = [w1].[WallpaperId]
LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [w].[Id] = [l].[WallpaperId]
ORDER BY [w].[PublishDate] DESC, [w].[Id], [w0].[Id], [u].[Id], [w1].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveToken], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HashedPassword], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastName], [t].[ProfileImage], [t].[RegisterDate], [t].[RoleId], [t].[Username], [t].[Id0], [t].[Title], [w].[Id], [w].[Description], [w].[DownloadsCount], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[Source], [w].[Title], [w].[UploaderId], [w].[UserId], [w].[ViewsCount], [w].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [w0].[Id], [w0].[Description], [w0].[DownloadsCount], [w0].[PublishDate], [w0].[Source], [w0].[Title], [w0].[UploaderId], [w0].[UserId], [w0].[ViewsCount], [w0].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [l].[Id], [l].[LikerId], [l].[WallpaperId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[ActiveToken], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[HashedPassword], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[ProfileImage], [u].[RegisterDate], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Username], [r].[Id] AS [Id0], [r].[Title]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r] ON [u].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
    WHERE [u].[Username] = @__decodedJWTModel_Username_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w] ON [t].[Id] = [w].[UploaderId]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w0] ON [t].[Id] = [w0].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [t].[Id] = [l].[LikerId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [w].[Id], [w0].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveToken], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HashedPassword], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastName], [t].[ProfileImage], [t].[RegisterDate], [t].[RoleId], [t].[Username], [t].[Id0], [t].[Title], [w].[Id], [w].[Description], [w].[DownloadsCount], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[Source], [w].[Title], [w].[UploaderId], [w].[UserId], [w].[ViewsCount], [w].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [w0].[Id], [w0].[Description], [w0].[DownloadsCount], [w0].[PublishDate], [w0].[Source], [w0].[Title], [w0].[UploaderId], [w0].[UserId], [w0].[ViewsCount], [w0].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [l].[Id], [l].[LikerId], [l].[WallpaperId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[ActiveToken], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[HashedPassword], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[ProfileImage], [u].[RegisterDate], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Username], [r].[Id] AS [Id0], [r].[Title]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r] ON [u].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
    WHERE [u].[Username] = @__decodedJWTModel_Username_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w] ON [t].[Id] = [w].[UploaderId]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w0] ON [t].[Id] = [w0].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [t].[Id] = [l].[LikerId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [w].[Id], [w0].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveToken], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HashedPassword], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastName], [t].[ProfileImage], [t].[RegisterDate], [t].[RoleId], [t].[Username], [t].[Id0], [t].[Title], [w].[Id], [w].[Description], [w].[DownloadsCount], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[Source], [w].[Title], [w].[UploaderId], [w].[UserId], [w].[ViewsCount], [w].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [w0].[Id], [w0].[Description], [w0].[DownloadsCount], [w0].[PublishDate], [w0].[Source], [w0].[Title], [w0].[UploaderId], [w0].[UserId], [w0].[ViewsCount], [w0].[WallpaperGenreCategoryId], [l].[Id], [l].[LikerId], [l].[WallpaperId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[ActiveToken], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[HashedPassword], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[ProfileImage], [u].[RegisterDate], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Username], [r].[Id] AS [Id0], [r].[Title]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]

    WHERE [u].[Username] = @__decodedJWTModel_Username_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w] ON [t].[Id] = [w].[UploaderId]
LEFT JOIN [Wallpapers] AS [w0] ON [t].[Id] = [w0].[UserId]
